      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.XrBOn1MueVB4u5sV]{Nanocyte Knack}</p>\n<p>Your nanites can alter their color and appearance, settling on your flesh in a variety of patterns and colors, providing you camouflage in your surroundings. When you attempt a @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.GMkLZsN3a7YPvA03.JournalEntryPage.5h3iePfJaeQMc3Qr]{Stealth} check while your @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.QoCQEVNtgMhsElwQ]{sheath array} is active, you can use a move action to increase the insight bonus to your Stealth check by 2 until the end of your turn. You can additionally use a @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.vh6n0Ad3lamOJXpV]{nanite surge} to hide in plain sight.</p>"
